source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_00<tab>Ponnixia has a dirty job, but some one has to do it.
target: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_00<tab>シルフの仮宿のポニシアは、冒険者に駆除してほしいものがあるようだ。

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_01<tab>Malicious sylphs are polluting the Sylphlands with a particularly unpleasant strain of the banestool, bringing considerable harm to the local flora and fauna. Slay two of the foul fungi to stave off further contamination of the forest.
target: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_01<tab>悪い子シルフの植えた<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2090B01 /var>の駆除を頼まれた。シルフ領の北部に生えている「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2090B01 /var>」を2つ、駆除しよう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_02<tab>The greater banestools will stink up the Sylphlands no more. Ponnixia will be pleased to hear of your success.
target: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_02<tab><var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2090B01 /var>を駆除した。シルフの仮宿のポニシアに報告しよう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_03<tab>Ponnixia appreciates your efforts in making the forest a more desirable place for her and her people to reside. She thanks you for your services and urges you to stay close by should she again require your aid.
target: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_SEQ_03<tab>ポニシアに報告した。ポニシアは、シルフ領の禍々しい空気も少しは浄化されるだろうと安堵した。またの機会に協力しよう。

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_000<tab><sigh> Touched ones are making a stink again, planting stink-spores across the Sylphlands.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_000冒険者、聞いてほちいのでふっち！
悪い子シルフがシルフ領に、
「」を植えちゃったのでふっち。

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_001<tab>The stink spreads, trees wither and die, and these ones' forest friends turn sick and angry. If some one does not put a stop to this, the forest will soon be uninhabitable by any one.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_001しかも、この「」は、
グングン育つやつで、かなり根が深くて強いでふっち。
……ここまで育つと、もはや叩き壊すしかないでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_002<tab>Brave one must slice up stink-spores and save the forest from a foul fate!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_002シルフ領に乗りこんで、
「」を叩いて枯らすのでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_003<tab>But brave one must be wary! Wherever stink-spores go, planting ones and stink-crazed creatures are sure to follow.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_003でも、注意なのでふっち！
「」の周りには、
瘴気が好きな魔物や、見張りの悪い子シルフがいるでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_005<tab>Brave one must slice up stink-spores and save the forest from a foul fate!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_005シルフ領に乗りこんで、
「」を叩いて枯らすのでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_006<tab>But brave one must be wary! Wherever stink-spores go, planting ones and stink-crazed creatures are sure to follow.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_006でも、注意なのでふっち！
「」の周りには、
瘴気の好きな魔物や、見張りの悪い子シルフがいるでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_010<tab>These ones thank you, brave one. Since brave one arrived here, the dark cloud hanging over the Sylphlands has begun to lift, little by little.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_010ごくろうさまなのでふっち！
これで、シルフ領のマガマガちい森も
少しは浄化されるのでふっち！

source: TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_011<tab>...But there is still much work to be done. Pray do not abandon these ones, brave one.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL210_01276_PONNIXIA_000_011でもまだまだ、森の調和には遠いでふっち。
また見かけたら、壊さなきゃなのでふっち！
